1. Descriere generală

    Acest proiect reprezinta un framework complet de testare automata, care acopera atat testarea interfetei de utilizator *UI*, dar si testarea serviciilor web *API*.

    * Aplicatia folosita atat pentru testarea UI, cat si pentru testarea API este: [Contact List](https://thinking-tester-contact-list.herokuapp.com/)


2. Tehnologii si instrumente folosite

    * Limbaj de programare: Java
    * UI Testing: Selenium
    * API Testing: RestAssured
    * Test Runner: TestNG
    * Design: Page Object Model
    * Build Tool: Maven
    * Rapoarte: Extent Reports


3. Arhitectura proiectului

    ~ [PAGES](https://github.com/chriss-zx/Proiect-automation-Nacea-Cristian/tree/df69d05b7a7d679ea7c72ccec692a495a0f81e9c/src/main/java/PAGES) - contine clasele *Page Object Model*
    ~ [utilities](https://github.com/chriss-zx/Proiect-automation-Nacea-Cristian/tree/df69d05b7a7d679ea7c72ccec692a495a0f81e9c/src/main/java/utilities) - contine clasele utilitare
    ~ [API](https://github.com/chriss-zx/Proiect-automation-Nacea-Cristian/tree/df69d05b7a7d679ea7c72ccec692a495a0f81e9c/src/test/java/API) - contine toate pachetele & clasele necesare API testing-ului.
    ~ [base](https://github.com/chriss-zx/Proiect-automation-Nacea-Cristian/tree/df69d05b7a7d679ea7c72ccec692a495a0f81e9c/src/test/java/base) - contine metodele de deschidere/inchidere a browser-ului
    ~ [listener](https://github.com/chriss-zx/Proiect-automation-Nacea-Cristian/tree/df69d05b7a7d679ea7c72ccec692a495a0f81e9c/src/test/java/listener) - contine clasa necesara raportului EXTENT
    ~ [tests](https://github.com/chriss-zx/Proiect-automation-Nacea-Cristian/tree/df69d05b7a7d679ea7c72ccec692a495a0f81e9c/src/test/java/tests) - contine clasele de test UI
    ~ [utils](https://github.com/chriss-zx/Proiect-automation-Nacea-Cristian/tree/df69d05b7a7d679ea7c72ccec692a495a0f81e9c/src/test/java/utils) - contine clasele necesare rapoartelor


4. Rularea testelor

    # Pentru rularea testelor este necesara instalarea JAVA JDK si MAVEN.
    # Descarcarea proiectului pe local.
    # Actualizarea dependintelor prin *mvn clean install* ( -DskipTests pentru o actualizare mai rapida, fara a rula toate testele)
    # Testele pot fi rulate separat (test/clasa/pachet) sau din terminal folosind *mvn test*




5. Continutul testelor

    # UI #
        ~ [LoginTests](https://github.com/chriss-zx/Proiect-automation-Nacea-Cristian/blob/df69d05b7a7d679ea7c72ccec692a495a0f81e9c/src/test/java/tests/LoginTests.java) - contine 4 teste (2 pentru signup si 2 pentru login)
        ~ [AddNewContact](https://github.com/chriss-zx/Proiect-automation-Nacea-Cristian/blob/df69d05b7a7d679ea7c72ccec692a495a0f81e9c/src/test/java/tests/AddNewContact.java) - contine 2 teste pentru adaugarea unui contact (date valide si date invalide)
        ~ [ContactDetails](https://github.com/chriss-zx/Proiect-automation-Nacea-Cristian/blob/df69d05b7a7d679ea7c72ccec692a495a0f81e9c/src/test/java/tests/ContactDetails.java) - contine 2 teste pentru editarea unui contact existent si un test pentru stergerea unui contact existent


    # API #
