                                                                    * un test signup
                                                                    * un test login
                                                                    * un test logout
                                                                    * un test delete user

        ~ [ContactsTests](https://github.com/chriss-zx/Proiect-automation-Nacea-Cristian/blob/df69d05b7a7d679ea7c72ccec692a495a0f81e9c/src/test/java/API/tests/ContactsTests.java) - contine 4 teste:
                                                                    * un test add contact
                                                                    * un test update contact
